plot: A doctor's wife in a small town tires of serving as his nurse and wants some "excitement", so she leaves for the big city to become a model. She rooms with a sophisticated city girl, Milly, and winds up having an affair with the lecherous owner of a gown shop. Her husband, meanwhile, has been made head of the local hospital, but when he tries to get his wife to come home, she demands a divorce, ...
